生的山口真帆事件中學習。AKB方面見狀即發聲明耍冧，承認標題惹來誤導，並將活動改為粉絲與成員為台上演出打氣。"},{"pid":"5d7da4e4fd968d66e0b09a943fda55972de10521","tid":1595662,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"536843e9afd21feb9d840b4df14cc809789a05a3","tid":1595662,"uid":205928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a01e6b0c0f3334d8e10ceabea8bfae0dfe0e55a1","tid":1595662,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190926/photo/bkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190926134214\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190926134214&h=8f002bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAKB近年開騷越玩越激，成員演出經常在台上剝衫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190926/photo/bkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190926134214\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190926134214&h=be181cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190926/photo/bkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190926134214\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190926134214&h=3f3d7994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190926/photo/bkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_07p.jpg?20190926134214\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190926%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190926125901731-0926_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20190926134214&h=e606b59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本大堆頭女團AKB48，近年聲勢大不如前，人氣早前早已被乃木坂46及欅坂46等女團趕過。為力挽狂瀾，近年AKB